00:18:44.290 --> 00:18:46.610
but if you think about
Nicholson's incarnations

00:18:46.610 --> 00:18:50.260
after that movie, you'll
understand how decisively

00:18:50.260 --> 00:18:54.930
and fully a new kind of actor
has emerged in the 1970s.

00:18:54.930 --> 00:18:59.100
And you might talk about some
of the other actors-- you

00:18:59.100 --> 00:19:02.960
can do the other
